snippet.title: Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney - Dual Destinies - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney - Dual Destinies is AVAILABLE NOW in the Nintendo 3DS eShop as well as on the iPad, iPhone, and iPod!

Download the first episode for FREE right here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id882362024

Fore more official Ace Attorney information: http://www.capcom-unity.com/ace_attorney/

Subscribe to the Official Capcom Unity Channel: 
http://bit.ly/Qjb2MV
